        Reverse Mortgage vs Selling: What Brisbane Seniors Need to Weigh Up
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        For older homeowners sitting on a valuable inner-east property, the choice between drawing equity through a reverse mortgage or selling and downsizing is one of the most consequential financial decisions of retirement. Here is how to think about it clearly.
      </p>
    </div>
